      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DON'T TELL MILLY (3) looks close to another win after finishing third last time (22.34) in a Grade 5 at this track. Winning claims. MIAMI RIOT (1) was below best at her last couple, the latest finishing fifth at this track, but was among the placings at this track three back. Rates a winning chance on best. WRINKLED HENRY (8) is rarely far away but tends to find one better, placing 11 from 20 starts. Finished in the minors last time when second (22.20) at this track making it back to back placings. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. Will give a great sight again. SKEDADDLE LULU (7) has been a model of consistency and deserves plenty of thought.",
